text: Hi Zoe! Just went through all your boards, it's looking really good! It did slightly confusing from slide 11 onwards but you mentioned you were still working on it. Despite that I can tell that it's definitely coming into focus now. I know that you're in a rush but do remember to slow it down when you can, rushing a project can lead to significant problems down the line! (I've been in that boat many _many_ times haha)
